x zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2532692\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 13, 2022</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104uhx1665702925014.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/uhx1665702925014.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/uhx1665702925014.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"uhx1665702925014\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Configure the Uniface Router for Multiple Tomcat Engines\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body taskbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">\n</p>\n<section><ol class=\"ol steps\"><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"uhx1665702925014__li_d23231e1_d23232e1_d23233e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">Edit the <span class=\"ph filepath\">urouter.asn</span> file to define a Uniface Router for each Tomcat server. For example:\n </span>\n<div class=\"itemgroup info\">\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">[SERVERS]\n; For Uniface WebApplication Server\nwasv1 = \"<var class=\"keyword varname\">UnifaceInstallDir</var>/common/bin/userver.exe\" \nwasv2 = \"<var class=\"keyword varname\">UnifaceInstallDir</var>/common/bin/userver.exe\"</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"uhx1665702925014__li_d23234e1_d23235e1_d23236e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">For each Tomcat server, modify the <code class=\"ph codeph\">web.xml</code> file in <span class=\"ph filepath\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">UnifaceInstallDir</var>/common/webapps/webapps/uniface/WEB-INF/</span> to point to the correct Uniface Router. Edit the MIDDLEWARE parameter of the WRD servlet; for example:\n </span>\n<div class=\"itemgroup info\">\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">&lt;init-param&gt;\n&lt;param-name&gt;MIDDLEWARE&lt;/param-name&gt;\n&lt;param-value&gt;UV8:localhost+13001|<var class=\"keyword varname\">Server1</var>/userver|userver|wasv1&lt;/param-value&gt;\n&lt;/init-param&gt;</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</li></ol></section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532692\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532692\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Configure the Uniface Router for Multiple Tomcat Engines Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 13, 2022 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Configure the Uniface Router for Multiple Tomcat Engines Edit the urouter.asn file to define a Uniface Router for each Tomcat server. For example: [SERVERS] ; For Uniface WebApplication Server wasv1 = \" UnifaceInstallDir /common/bin/userver.exe\" wasv2 = \" UnifaceInstallDir /common/bin/userver.exe\" Copy For each Tomcat server, modify the web.xml file in UnifaceInstallDir /common/webapps/webapps/uniface/WEB-INF/ to point to the correct Uniface Router. Edit the MIDDLEWARE parameter of the WRD servlet; for example: <init-param> <param-name>MIDDLEWARE</param-name> <param-value>UV8:localhost+13001| Server1 /userver|userver|wasv1</param-value> </init-param> Copy Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}